      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`For each ad $i$ we take a random draw from the distribution below:`}</p>
        <ul parentName="li">
          <li parentName="ul">{`$\\theta_i(n)=\\beta(N_i^1(n)+1,N_i^0(n)+1)$`}</li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li parentName="ol">
        <p parentName="li">{`We selet the ad that has the highest $\\theta_i(n)$ `}</p>
