    <p>{`What is a convolution in intuitive terms? We have an `}<strong parentName="p">{`input image`}</strong>{` and a `}<strong parentName="p">{`feature detector`}</strong>{`. Feature detector can also be known as a `}<em parentName="p">{`kernal`}</em>{` or a `}<em parentName="p">{`filter`}</em>{`.`}</p>
